By clicking Continue, Microsoft will send limited Xbox account information to Barclays to assist with your application. This includes contact details to prefill your application and information about your engagement with Xbox, including the duration of your Xbox account and when you last made a Microsoft purchase. Data provided to Barclays in your credit card application or after becoming a cardmember is governed by Barclays Privacy Policy and credit card Terms and Conditions. If you click Cancel, the data will not be sent.
